  <brief_title>Impact of Conservative Treatment by Custom-made Orthoses in Patients With Haemophilic Ankle Arthropathy</brief_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Cliniques universitaires Saint-Luc- Université Catholique de Louvain</agency>
